	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />¿No te parece<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 /> la repera limonera?<pageBreak /><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Bueeeno. Será que ya tienes
